Subject: [PATCH 1/3] feat: standardize transactional UI and multi-source merge

- Redesigned transaction form macros for uniform layout and UX.
- Implemented smart-select across Purchases, Sales, and Inventory modules.
- Added two-step workflow for merging multiple source documents.
- Renamed adjustment-negative routes to generic inventory-issue.
- Extended document flow API with party filtering support.
- Added exhaustive E2E tests for transactional UI logic.
